Revision history for MetaCPAN-Client-Pod-PDF

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

0.02    2020-04-13
	- Update MakeFile with missing dependency
	- Justify align 'text' content

0.03    2020-04-13
	- Add a 'raw' method that accepts a string of valid POD markup to convert into a PDF.
	- Add a boolean hook to allow for the stringified version of the PDF to be returned.
